csmLanMdmDiagAdminStatus.name: csmLanMdmDiagAdminStatus
csmLanMdmDiagAdminStatus.description: The administrative status of CSM modem diag table. The value 'enabled' enables csmLanModemDiagTable and 'disabled' stops csmLanModemDiagTable from continuing collecting diagnostic information. GenError is returned when trying to enable this object if no JDEC card present. This object can also be set via parameter 'cms-modem-diag' in TNT snmp profile.
